  Body (Conjunction of Literals) Initialized to True
  Old Variables
       Operators:Add a new literal   Preds*(vars+arity-1)*arity
 
  Using every predicate, and every way of inserting New and Old Variables
  Produces a Set of Positive Tuples  (P1), Negative Tuples  (N1),  Body, Variables
